---
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{SITE_TITLE}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="layout">
			<Sidebar />
			<div class="content">
				<h1>안녕하세요.<br />기록하며 성장하는 whiteblack 입니다.</h1>
				<p class="intro">
					Business Management를 전공하고 Data Science를 부전공하며,
					Brigham Young University - Idaho 졸업했습니다<br />
					데이터베이스/백엔드/프론트엔드까지 폭넓게 학습한 내용을 이곳에 TIL(Today I Learned) 형태로 기록합니다.
				</p>

				<hr />

				<h2>현재 학습중</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>HTML/CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript</li>
					<li>React / Vue / Angular</li>
					<li>Python, SQL (Oracle, MySQL, PostgreSQL, BigQuery 등)</li>
					<li>Django, Nest.js</li>
					<li>Machine Learning / Deep Learning / NLP / LangChain, LangGraph</li>
				</ul>

				<hr />

				<h2>2026 활동</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>1. 기록 </li>
					<li>2. 면접 </li>
					<li>3. 코테 </li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />

		<style>
			.layout {
				display: flex;
				width: 960px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				gap: 3em;
				padding-top: 2em;
			}
			.content {
				flex: 1;
			}
			h1 {
				font-size: 2rem;
				line-height: 1.4;
				margin-bottom: 1em;
			}
			.intro {
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				line-height: 1.7;
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
				margin-bottom: 2em;
			}
			h2 {
				margin-top: 1.5em;
			}
			ul {
				line-height: 1.9;
			}
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.layout {
					flex-direction: column;
					width: 100%;
					padding: 1em;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>